This package provides a Zig build system for aria2. The upstream aria2 source
code is licensed under GPL-2.0-or-later. See https://github.com/aria2/aria2 for
the upstream project and its license.

The Zig build scripts, configuration, and patches in this repository are
licensed under MIT (above). When you build aria2 using this package, the
resulting binary combines MIT-licensed build code with GPL-2.0-or-licensed
upstream code.
